OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers will
OL,6,Fgradually die out this evening.
OL,7,FTurning cloudier through the early
OL,8,Fhours, with rain spreading in from the
OL,9,Fwest towards the end of the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FRather cloudy with mostly
OL,12,Flight rain in the morning. Showers or
OL,13,Flonger spells of rain following on,
OL,14,Fsome of which may be on the heavy side.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,17,FVariable cloud with showers or a few
OL,18,Flonger spells of rain, some of which
OL,19,Fmay be on the heavy side. Often warm
OL,20,Fin any sunny spells around the Moray
OL,21,FFirth.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
